== Spell Effectiveness ==

=== Damage Formula ===

```
Base Damage = Spell Power + (Magic Stat / 4)
Final Damage = Base × Elemental Modifier

Elemental Modifier:
  Weakness = 2.0
  Normal = 1.0
  Resist = 0.5
  Immune = 0.0
```

=== Healing Formula ===

```
Heal Amount = Spell Power + (Magic Stat / 2)
```

== Battle Strategy ==

=== Spell Priority ===

'''Early Game (Foresta):'''
1. Cure for healing
2. Fire for damage
3. Physical when MP low

'''Mid Game (Aquaria-Fireburg):'''
1. Blizzard for groups
2. Thunder for water foes
3. Heal for emergency

'''Late Game (Windia-Doom):'''
1. Meteor for groups
2. Flare for bosses
3. White for undead

=== MP Conservation ===

* Use physical attacks on weak enemies
* Save powerful spells for bosses
* Use weapon spell effects when available
* Rest at inns before bosses

